createERC20(string,string,uint256,uint25.details: This function deploys a new ERC20 token contract and registers the caller as the owner of the token in the `tokenOwners` mapping.

params.maxSupply: The maximum number of ERC20 tokens that can be minted
params.name: The name of the ERC20 token
params.symbol: The symbol of the ERC20 token
params.tokenPrice: The price per ERC20 token in Wei

returns.token: The address of the created ERC20 token contract

createERC721(string,string,uint256,uint2.details: This function deploys a new ERC721 token contract and registers the caller as the owner of the token in the `tokenOwners` mapping.

params.baseURI: The base URI for ERC721 token metadata
params.maxSupply: The maximum number of ERC721 tokens that can be minted
params.name: The name of the ERC721 token
params.symbol: The symbol of the ERC721 token
params.tokenPrice: The price per ERC721 token in Wei

returns.token: The address of the created ERC721 token contract

createERC20(string,string,uint256,uint25.notice: Creates a new ERC20 token and registers it

createERC721(string,string,uint256,uint2.notice: Creates a new ERC721 token and registers it
